End Process

Process called "translate_schema_definition" takes node as Integer returns Integer:
    Note: Translate GQL_SCHEMA_DEF to HIR

    Let dict be proc create_dictionary

    Let type_key be proc create_string from StringCore with "type"
    Let type_value be proc create_string from StringCore with "schema"
    proc dict_set with dict, type_key, type_value

